<%- include("partials/header") -%>

</head>

<body>
  <div id="loadOverlay" style="background-color:#333; position:sticky; top:0px; left:0px; width:100%; height:100vh; z-index:2000;">
  </div>
  <div class="site-wrapper">
    <header class="on-load">
      <a name=#top></a>
      <img class="header-logo" src="./public/images/homepage/the_writing_doctor_logo.jpg" alt="The Writing Doctor Logo" loading="lazy" style="max-width: 100px;">
      <navbar-component></navbar-component>
    </header>

    <main class="about">
      <div class="hero hero-about">
        <div class="hero-main">
          <div class="hero-slogan">
            <h1>
              WRITING IS
              <br>
              THE BEST
              <br>
              MEDICINE
            </h1>
            <h2 class>Allow me to introduce myself</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-image">
            <img class="silohoutte" src="./public/images/homepage/man_standing_silohoutte.png" alt="Man Standing Silohouette">
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
      <div class="content-section top-section-about">
        <div class="line line-about-me">
        </div>

        <div class="content">

          <div class="headings">
            <h2>HI THERE. I'M JOE NIGHTINGALE, AKA THE <span class="highlight-blue"> WRITING DOCTOR.</span></h2>
            <p>That's not a fake title. I'm the real deal. A <em>bona fide</em> medical doctor - I've even got the stethoscope to prove it.</p>

          </div>
          <div class="bio">
            <img class="bio-image" src="./public/images/about/temp_stethoscope_image.jpg" alt="">
            <div class="bio-text">
             
              <p class="align-left">Only these days, I'm not treating patients on the wards... </p>
              <p class=""> ...I'm saving nonprofits and businesses from the clutches of bad content. I <span class="highlight-bold">diagnose</span> their problems and <span class="highlight-bold">prescribe</span> a dose of content guaranteed to cure.
              </p>
              <p>I've worked with businesses across all industries, including <span class="highlight-bold">beauty products, educational services, cosmetics, healthcare, clinical trials, beard oils, foodstuffs, pet toys</span>, and more.</p>
              <p>Sounds like a lot? It's not. It's all the same thing: capturing your customers attention and keeping them coming back. That's earned me <span class="highlight-bold">hundreds of satisfied businesses</span> and thousands of eager readers.</p>
              <p>Because I go above and beyond. Because I want you to be 100% satisfied and won't rest until your readers or customers are too.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>


      <div class="content-section middle-section middle-section-about">
        <div class="content">                
          <div class="testimonial">
            <i class="fas fa-quote-left highlight-yellow"></i>
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <h2>I JUMPED POSITION FROM <span class="highlight-yellow">54TH PLACE</span> TO <span class="highlight-yellow">4TH PLACE</SPan> IN GOOGLE WITH ONE OF JOE'S ARTICLES</h2>
              <h3 class="testimonial-author"> Bibi Burness</h3>
              <h3 class="testimonial-author-title highlight-yellow">SEO Expert & Business Owner</h3>
            </div>
            <i class="fas fa-quote-right highlight-yellow""></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="carousel" class="content-section carousel carousel-promises">
        <div class="line line-about-me">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
          <h2>
            EVERY ORDER COMES WITH FIVE PROMISES<span class="highlight-yellow">.</span>
          </h2>
          <div class="promises-inner">

            <div class="left-arrow arrows">
              <div class="testimonial-arrows">
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-arrows">
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-left"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
            <img class="carousel-item" src="./public/images/about/1_carousel.png" alt="Search Engine Optimised">
            <img class="carousel-item hidden" src="./public/images/about/2_carousel.png" alt="Search Engine Optimised">
            <img class="carousel-item hidden" src="./public/images/about/3_carousel.png" alt="Search Engine Optimised">
            <img class="carousel-item hidden" src="./public/images/about/4_carousel.png" alt="Search Engine Optimised">
            <img class="carousel-item hidden" src="./public/images/about/5_carousel.png" alt="Search Engine Optimised">
            <div class="right-arrow arrows">
              <div class="testimonial-arrows">
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
              </div>
              <div class="testimonial-arrows">
                <i class="fas fa-chevron-right"></i>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    <div class="">

      <div class="logo-section">
        <div class="line line-about-me">
        </div>
        <h2>EXPERIENCE THE SUCCESS OF <br> QUALITY CONTENT<SPAN CLASS="highlight-yellow">.</SPAN></h2>
        <div class="logos">   
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="./public/images/homepage/beard_sorcery_logo.png" alt="Beard Sorcery Logo" loading="lazy">
            <h3>+200 Satisfied Customers and Businesses</h3>
            <p>From insurance companies to beard oil companies, I've never has a bad review. WIll you be the next satisfied client?</p>
          </div>
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="./public/images/homepage/teonan_logo.png" alt="Beard Sorcery Logo">
            <h3>+100,000 Reads and Views on Medium.com</h3>
            <p>With an active reader base, my articles regularly receive tens of thousands of reads and views, making me a Top Science Writer.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="./public/images/homepage/beard_sorcery_logo.png" alt="Beard Sorcery Logo" loading="lazy">
            <h3>Creative & Innovative Writing</h3>
            <p>If you've got a passion for your product, I'll amplify it. Because that's what sells... personality, quality, originality.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="icon">
            <img src="./public/images/homepage/beard_sorcery_logo.png" alt="Beard Sorcery Logo" loading="lazy">
            <h3>Scientific and Medical Expertise</h3>
            <p>As a qualified doctor with a Masters in Ecology, there's no one better to research scientific content.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>      
    </div>

     



      <div class="signup-container">
      <%- include("partials/signup") -%>
      <div class="book container">
        <div class="book-inner">
          <h2 class="book-today">Book <br> Today</h2>
          <img src="./public/images/homepage/book.png" alt="Book Picture">
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </main>



  <%- include("partials/footer") -%>
</div>
</body>
<script type="module" src="public/module.js"></script>
<script type="module" src="public/carousel.js"></script>
<script type="module" src="public/hide-header.js"></script>
</html>
